law.history: Repealed 1952 Ky. Acts ch. 134, sec. 63, effective June 19, 1952. -- Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. secs. 1486b-48, 1486b-50.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: New registration required when name changed; transfer of registration on change of residence; utility companies to report changes of address of customers.
